curam.common.util.xml.dom.output

Class XMLOutputter

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.common.util.xml.dom.output.XMLOutputter

  • public class XMLOutputter
extends java.lang.Object
    XMLOutputter takes a DOM tree and formats it to a stream as XML. This class wraps a CustomXMLWriter (which extends a dom4j XMLWriter).

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      XMLOutputter()
      Constructs a default XML writer.

      Constructs an XML writer with the given formatter.
